  <brief_title>Comparison of Neo-adjuvant Weekly Paclitaxel With or Without Carboplatin in Early Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Randomized Clinical Trial of Neo-adjuvant Weekly Paclitaxel With or Without Carboplatin in Early Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
