  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether neo-adjuvant weekly paclitaxel with
      carboplatin is better than paclitaxel alone in efficiency and safety in early breast cancer,
      and to explore whether ultrasound and magnetic resonance imaging can predict the efficiency
      of neo-adjuvant chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
